{"tid":1415424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如何真正咁we connect","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:09.000Z","uid":193376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7af91796ea8389144e0b19c5c48802c8e0c6a10","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"有野補充 想重post<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n希望大家聽下我嘅愚見<br />\n唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 前線同後防嘅溝通不足</span><br />\n有時<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非唔明白前線嘅諗法</span><br />\nEg 點解要守一個地方/ 封路<br />\n所以就<span style=\"color: gold;\">好難叫郁佢地幫手</span> <br />\n但如果你地比佢清楚了解前線嘅動機 <br />\n佢地一定唔好就手旁觀<br />\n同一時間 希望和理非明白人多更安全嘅道理<br />\n願意當有人要幫手時會一齊去<br />\n<br />\n另外 <span style=\"color: gold;\">尊重前線嘅前設係要確保佢地有足夠資訊</span><br />\n佢地未必好似和理非咁多時間睇tg/ lihkg<br />\n所以未掌握到成個局面<br />\n咁樣會令佢地好易身陷險境<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">依個時候可以搵和理非做哨兵傳話</span><br />\n比前線有更多掌握下做決定<br />\n減低送頭機會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 注意語氣</span><br />\n有時啲示威者叫人幫手 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但無人理時就會有少少燥</span><br />\n(例如: 你地真係唔理呼籲咖喎，叫你地出去幫手但你坐係度有乜用?)<br />\n或者<span style=\"color: gold;\">同 &lsquo;不明白我地動機&rsquo; 嘅市民溝通時<br />\n會有種 &lsquo;示威者係為香港人而戰&rsquo;嘅優越感</span> (例如 你嘅犧牲唔比得上我地嘅犧牲) 嘅語氣談判<br />\n咁樣會令人無好感 <br />\n示威者之間亦應該互相提醒 叫大家克制啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. Focus翻如何解決，而非追究責任</span><br />\n有時啲野發生咗咁都無辨法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">預其花時間問個究竟 <br />\n不如爭分奪秒一齊傾點解決</span><br />\n只要下次唔好再錯就可以了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">最後 連登其實係個溫室</span><br />\n好多時都只聽到某一方嘅意見<br />\n就今次嘅事為例<br />\n連登仔只會差唔多一面倒咁支持示威者嘅行為<br />\n但無可否認 <br />\n有啲行為未必完全得到市民嘅支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">特別係當依度缺乏上一代嘅年齡層<br />\n我地根本唔太掌握佢地諗法<br />\n唔可以assume佢地一定諒解我地</span><br />\n(以我深黃老豆為例 佢對有啲事情都未能完全理解 ，Eg. 點解要封路阻人放工)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實民意係好撚重要</span></span><br />\n所以希望大家多聽各方嘅睇法同對我地行為嘅意見<br />\n唔好學林奠咁<br />\n只會活係自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"248677c4a69235ea2f47c0e43b76858551f1bc5d","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e73c5cacf06174b927a6d9e6a3b7a1be978b3fe9","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9b149feaf0a65f878ad2eb8ef998ab9dbbd8b6aa","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"17b4c7860e70f4edfa3de7cd16115ff258fc2dfd","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"393d2ba8d577a0c6a276d1248623eee49643ecfa","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4978a6199c7e04d01b518eaa2723623d80355d1c","tid":1415424,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"23f73172bfdd64fce869300ab3134001cab07a0c","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1836beb69e8c105027bd9b55e71642a8b0aabee3","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6d09e8e854f7bbfabae8cab3520ee59c62487ea0","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7ebdd826121f9c564f0180f9b1e576b8598a5a6c","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8acefa020c0dccce039bd577b5a28870dabf6d23","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f855515592f787d672218f291e58b07df738035a","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c167089b49996296e265789a7eb4c407495c99cd","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8094c80bbcd3d5509ade3bfe27aec18df1fc9da7","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7eb260f81ad1ad9a6951a7f5517f8fae1329123e","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"06d18328f290e497d41dd7c76dfe2d33bba1f34a","tid":1415424,"uid":193376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}